h2 Examples
p.-text
  | To render a textarea, apply the class <code>a-input</code> to a <code>textarea</code>.

h3 Base
.example.-mb--3
  .-p--3
    .m-form__item(style="max-width:30rem")
      label.a-label(for="example__base") Label
      textarea.a-input(id="example__base") Sample text
  :code(lang="html")
    <div class="m-form__item">
      <label class="a-label" for="example__base">Label</label>
      <textarea class="a-input" id="example__base">
        Sample text
      </textarea>
    </div>

